薄彼</blockquote><br />\n通巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 小心射唔出精加你入5毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咪撚扮熟"},{"pid":"a49c439c435bcb6cd9c125a16f84e64fd9bee8a5","tid":442251,"uid":86841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T12:28:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c0ed1f9cb634b240545c2662c8ca98b1d130c500","tid":442251,"uid":85163,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T12:28:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a5db0a88999ad63ca74a5155a1de88459d368e14","tid":442251,"uid":46644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T12:29:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"39eaa6c2c3177852913cbec910f6ea54ea82306a","tid":442251,"uid":86841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T12:30:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e0a363cc8544312c5190527f00533824e25104b2","tid":442251,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T12:32:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/415309/page/1?ref=android\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/415309/page/1?ref=android</a><br />\n<br />\n唔係話唔想撐<br />\n但濕巴玩到咁點會唔bam<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n三色貓就唔使bam?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n嗰行為同嚴重性都唔同<br />\n<br />\n三色貓我所見係開膠post加自推十次八次<br />\n<br />\n或者貼文狙擊人<br />\n<br />\n哩樣好多人包括你我都有做 （如果仲有其他請你更正）<br />\n<br />\n濕巴講到出口，做埋出黎，係要洗到嗰post冇人討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n問心有冇五毛做到咁呢？<br />\n<br />\n有一個，民國復興，所以咪bam左<br />\n<br />\n僅以哩個case計我睇唔到admin有不公平<br />\n<br />\n你不能期望admin因為政治或其他立場而厚此薄彼</blockquote><br />\n通巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 小心射唔出精加你入5毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咪撚扮熟</blockquote><br />\n只係多謝你公正講出事實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n另一事實就係你係高登打手加五毛<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/21/203146_8b9f3acea9f0802c00af7da68e8e440e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F21%2F203146_8b9f3acea9f0802c00af7da68e8e440e.jpg&h=d76affc9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ec53933b80d0236822be283f26a3ef8f5c962111","tid":442251,"uid":46644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T12:32:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b24b6b7332a712e17e6e91bd3399ebfc51c73886","tid":442251,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T16:18:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f42f548c0322602b8b8169087da950eb9dd95121","tid":442251,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T16:20:10.000Z","msg":"應該cc台獨立"},{"pid":"76f35d80abd38954680fb92f98d427430a60a447","tid":442251,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T17:03:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>admin早晨</blockquote><br />\nadmin晚安"},{"pid":"43c920a01693b32c81099537464ac6e655c5d3a1","tid":442251,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T03:34:03.000Z","msg":"Oct 21近期活躍五毛<br />\n0三色貓<br />\n1JR<br />\n2群龍共舞<br />\n3法國佬巫斯義=香港鍵國<br />\n4真律師何君堯<br />\n5Romanov<br />\n6吾系甘開心牙<br />\n7優美開始<br />\n8dewi<br />\n9bb chu<br />\n10RedBaron<br />\n11蘇麗珊<br />\n12十卜ching"},{"pid":"31d18b35eef377d89ddae07360a32811aa186902","tid":442251,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedB